### Facet Eval API — VS Code REST Client
### Install: "REST Client" extension by Humao
### Usage: Click "Send Request" above any request block

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

###
# 1. Health check — is Ollama up and model loaded?
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###
# 2. List all facets
GET {{baseUrl}}/facets

###
# 3. List facets filtered by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/facets?category=emotional

###
# 4. List hard-difficulty facets only
GET {{baseUrl}}/facets?difficulty=hard

###
# 5. Score a conversation — emotional distress case
POST {{baseUrl}}/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversation": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "I've been really struggling lately. Nothing I do seems good enough and I'm exhausted all the time."},
    {"role": "assistant", "content": "That sounds really hard. It takes courage to say that. What's been weighing on you most?"},
    {"role": "user", "content": "Everything honestly. Work, relationships, money. I just don't see the point sometimes."}
  ],
  "turn_index": 0,
  "facet_categories": ["emotional"]
}

###
# 6. Score only linguistic facets on turn 1 (assistant response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversation": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Can you explain how neural networks work?"},
    {"role": "assistant", "content": "Sure! A neural network is a system loosely inspired by the brain. It consists of layers of nodes, or neurons, that transform input data step by step into a final output. Each connection between nodes has a weight that gets adjusted during training to minimise prediction error."}
  ],
  "turn_index": 1,
  "facet_categories": ["linguistic", "cognitive"]
}

###
# 7. Score all facets — anger/hostility case
POST {{baseUrl}}/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversation": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "My coworker took credit for my project AGAIN. I am so done with this. I want to confront him in front of the whole team."}
  ],
  "turn_index": -1
}

###
# 8. Score high-conscientiousness case
POST {{baseUrl}}/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversation": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "I've mapped out the next six weeks of the project with milestones, risk flags, and buffer time for each stage. I also prepared three scenarios — optimistic, realistic, and worst-case — with contingency plans written for each."}
  ],
  "turn_index": -1,
  "facet_categories": ["behavioral", "professional", "cognitive"]
}
